## Dark Mode

Use Tailwind's `dark:` prefix for dark mode overrides:

```jsx
className="bg-canvas-50 dark:bg-cosmos-200"
className="text-ink-600 dark:text-ink-50"
className="border-border-primary dark:border-cosmos-50"
```

Theme is toggled via `.dark` class on `<html>` element.

